sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>(Jupyter Notebook)
    participant SDK as CodeFlare SDK<br/>(Python Client)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Service<br/>10001/TCP mTLS
    participant Dashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP
    participant Gateway as RHOAI Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Gateway: Flow 1: Create and Connect to Ray Cluster

    User->>SDK: Cluster(ClusterConfiguration(...))
    SDK->>K8sAPI: POST ray.io/v1/rayclusters<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OIDC / OAuth
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: RayCluster CR created
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Watch ray.io/v1/rayclusters
    Note over KubeRay: Reconciles into Ray<br/>head/worker pods

    SDK->>K8sAPI: GET secrets (ca-secret-*)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: CA cert + private key

    Note over SDK: Generates RSA-3072 client cert<br/>locally with x509v3 extensions<br/>Stores at ~/.local/share/codeflare/tls/<br/>Permissions: 0600

    SDK->>RayHead: ray://{cluster}-head-svc.{ns}.svc:10001<br/>Protocol: Ray Client<br/>Auth: mTLS client certificate
    RayHead-->>SDK: Connection established

    Note over User,Gateway: Flow 2: Submit RayJob via KubeRay

    User->>SDK: RayJob(ManagedClusterConfig(...))
    SDK->>SDK: Package working_dir into zip<br/>Validate Ray version (2.54.1)

    SDK->>K8sAPI: POST v1/secrets ({rayjob}-files)<br/>Contains: entrypoint + working_dir zip<br/>OwnerRef: RayJob CR
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: Secret created

    SDK->>K8sAPI: POST ray.io/v1/rayjobs<br/>Labels: kueue queue, priority class<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: RayJob CR created
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Watch ray.io/v1/rayjobs
    Note over KubeRay: Creates Ray cluster,<br/>submits job to Ray

    loop Poll job status
        SDK->>K8sAPI: GET ray.io/v1/rayjobs/{name}<br/>Check: jobDeploymentStatus
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: Status update
    end

    Note over User,Gateway: Flow 3: Dashboard URL Resolution (RHOAI 3.x)

    User->>SDK: cluster.dashboard_uri()
    SDK->>K8sAPI: LIST gateway.networking.k8s.io/v1/httproutes<br/>Label: ray.io/cluster-name={name}
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: HTTPRoute list

    alt HTTPRoute found (RHOAI 3.x)
        SDK->>K8sAPI: GET gateway.networking.k8s.io/v1/gateways/{ref}<br/>Extract: hostname from spec.listeners
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: Gateway CR
        SDK-->>User: https://{hostname}/ray/{ns}/{cluster}
    else Fallback: OpenShift Route
        SDK->>K8sAPI: GET route.openshift.io/v1/routes<br/>Name: ray-dashboard-{cluster}
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: Route CR
        SDK-->>User: https://{route-host}
    else Fallback: Kubernetes Ingress
        SDK->>K8sAPI: GET networking.k8s.io/v1/ingresses<br/>Name: ray-dashboard-{cluster}
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: Ingress CR
        SDK-->>User: http(s)://{ingress-host}
    end

    User->>Gateway: Open dashboard in browser<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token
    Gateway->>Dashboard: Forward to Ray Dashboard
    Dashboard-->>Gateway: Dashboard UI
    Gateway-->>User: Dashboard response
